1. Can nhac:
    1.1. Them bien timeout cho thoi gian nhan giu nut config, neu nut bi nhan qua
    10s thi khong nhan trang thai nhan giu cua nut nua, cu the trong truong hop
    nguoi dung "chot nhan ra" khong muon cho thiet bi thoat mang va muon huy thao 
    tac do.
    => Luon cho nguoi dung co kha nang huy mot thao tac nao do.
2. Bo sung
	2.1. Chinh lai thong so loai cam bien cho dung, cam bien chuyen dong co ma rieng,
	cam bien vo cua kinh co ma rieng